        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5641",
        "content": "Clearly, if one was called upon to simplify this, he would retain the two small circles joined side by side at the top, and would indicate the lower circle with a line or dash.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
